text: La Baroche is a municipality in the district of Porrentruy in the canton of Jura in Switzerland. On 1 January 2009, the former municipalities of Asuel, Charmoille, Fregiécourt, Miécourt and Pleujouse merged into the new municipality of La Baroche. == References == == Other websites == * Category:2009 establishments in Switzerland Category:Municipalities in Porrentruy
